article_id:1167,category_name:News,title_name:Announcing Gala Dragalia!,image_path:,message:<div>Gala Dragalia will start <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>What is Gala Dragalia?</div><div>・The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons will be boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5★ summon or 5★ featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia event duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585807140"></span></div><div><br></div><div>The featured Gala Dragalia adventurer is detailed below.</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia adventurer:</div><div>
