<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/a2241ae1de30904a24117f1388bd71782.png"></span><span>Reduced Defense Punisher +30%</span></dt><dd><div>Increases damage to enemies with reduced<br>defense by 30%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/bd7de81c28d0b9c93b0edbfc86b0cb6a2.png"></span><span>Guardian Shadow II</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to blindness<br>and paralysis by 100%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/d3edea4a52a651ab75575f278704b8a82.png"></span><span>Poisoned Punisher +30%</span></dt><dd><div>Increases damage to poisoned enemies by 30%.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>・The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities, and represent the adventurer at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unlocked, not the stats when first obtained.</div><div>・Adventurers with the same name cannot be put into the same team.</div><div>・ Chain co-abilities are co-abilities that were added in Ver.1.18.0 and are not available in versions before Ver.1.18.0.</div><div><br></div><div>Adventurer characteristics:<br>Instead of skill gauges, Gala Alex features a new functionality called the Skill Reservoir, which is consumed when she uses skills.<br>Note: This does not apply to weapon skills.<br><br>The Skill Reservoir fills as you hit enemies with attacks, and it is possible to fill it up enough to unleash skills up to three times. Each use of Alex&#39;s Crisis Edge and Umbral Erasure skills decreases the Skill Reservoir by one level, and hitting enemies with skills consecutively activates Skill Chain. When Skill Chain activates, enemies will suffer additional effects and damage based on the skill combination and the state of the enemy.</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/9b5034aa85befa7183660c01d20afa9c.jpg"></div><div><br></div><div>If Skill Chain can be used, the frame around the skill icon will glow blue.<br><br>▼Skill Chain example using Crisis Edge<br>1st use:<br>The Crisis Edge skill is used.<br>&rArr;The target takes shadow damage and enemy defense is decreased.<br><br>2nd use:<br>The following Skill Chains may occur, depending on the state of the enemy and the skill that is used.<br><br>(a) The Crisis Edge skill is used and Skill Chain activates.<br>&rArr;Enemies directly ahead take shadow damage (enemies with decreased defense take extra damage).<br>&rArr;The skill deals bonus damage (enemies with decreased defense take extra damage).<br><br>(b) The Umbral Erasure skill is used while the target is under the effects of a buff (condition 1), and Skill Chain activates.<br>&rArr;The target takes shadow damage and one buff effect ends.<br>&rArr;The skill deals bonus damage (enemies afflicted with poison take extra damage).<br><br>(c) The Umbral Erasure skill is used while the target is in the break state (condition 2), and Skill Chain activates.<br>&rArr;The target takes shadow damage (enemies in the break state take extra damage).<br>&rArr;The skill deals bonus damage (enemies in the break state take extra damage).<br><br>Note: If the target meets both condition 1 and condition 2, then condition 1 will be prioritized.<br><br>▼Skill Chain example using Umbral Erasure<br>1st use:<br>The Umbral Erasure skill is used.<br>&rArr;The target takes shadow damage and is afflicted with poison.<br><br>2nd use:<br>The following Skill Chains may occur, depending on the state of the enemy and the skill that is used.<br><br>(a) The Umbral Erasure skill is used and Skill Chain activates.<br>&rArr;The target takes shadow damage (enemies afflicted with poison take extra damage).<br>&rArr;The skill deals bonus damage (enemies afflicted with poison take extra damage).<br><br>(b) The Crisis Edge skill is used while the target is under the effects of a buff (condition 1), and Skill Chain activates.<br>&rArr;The target takes shadow damage and one buff effect ends.<br>&rArr;The skill deals bonus damage (enemies with decreased defense take extra damage).<br><br>(c) The Crisis Edge skill is used while the target is in the break state (condition 2), and Skill Chain activates.<br>&rArr;The target takes shadow damage (enemies in the break state take extra damage).<br>&rArr;The skill deals bonus damage (enemies in the break state take extra damage).<br><br>Note: If the target meets both condition 1 and condition 2, then condition 1 will be prioritized.</div><div><br></div><div>Note:</div><div>For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1585105200,update_time1585105633